message.body: Hey Lindsey! Are you interested in swimming either tomorrow or Friday around 5:30? If not, maybe we could go next week?
Let's do Friday! Im teaching tmw evening until 10 but friday would be awesome!
Yay!! I can meet you either at your place or at the Y. Just let me know what's easiest for you.
Let's walk over together! Come to my place and we can take a walk! Let me make sure the lanes are open hang on.
I can meet later if necessary
They don't open til about 6:45 but you could come here and hang and we can have a tea before heading over. I think the swim team has practice 4-6:30
Or we can sauna before and after :)
Haha, sounds good! I will come to your place after work and we can decide then if we want to be extra extra relaxed. Looking forward to it!!
Lol. Awesome. I am also looking forward to it!
